# Test your FastAPI endpoints

### Root
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

### Hello endpoint (prueba)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/hello/User
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check del servicio OCR
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Subir imagen
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/documento.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Extraer texto de imagen local
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/extract?image_path=./uploads/documento.jpg
Accept: application/json

###

### Extraer texto desde URL
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/extract-from-url?image_url=https://example.com/documento.jpg
Accept: application/json

###

### Extraer campos de DUI (POST multipart)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/extract-dui
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="dui.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/dui.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Extraer campos de Licencia de Conducir (POST multipart)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/extract-license
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="licencia.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/licencia.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Validar documento DUI
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/validate-document?document_type=dui
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="dui.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/dui.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Validar documento Licencia
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/validate-document?document_type=license
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="licencia.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/licencia.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Procesar múltiples imágenes en lote
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ocr/batch-process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="doc1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/doc1.jpg
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="doc2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/doc2.jpg
--boundary--

###

